high_descs: Walk ahead and slightly left to face the toaster.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Place the tomato in the fridge in front of the white plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a fridge.

high_descs: move forward to the counter that is to the left of the refrigerator
pick up the tomato from the counter that is to the right of the green cup
turn left and move forward to the microwave
open the microwave door, put the tomato in to the microwave, close the door, turn on the microwave for three seconds, open the door and remove the tomato
turn around and move forward to the refrigerator on the left, turn to face the fridge
open the fridge doors and put the tomato on the right side in front of the white plate and close the doors
anns.task_desc: put a cooked tomato in to the refrigerator

high_descs: Walk and stand in front of the toaster that's to the left of the fridge that's right in front of you.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of the toaster.
Turn left and walk to the microwave that's in front of you.
Cook the tomato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge and when you get to it turn left to face it.
Put the tomato in the fridge under the white plate on the bottom shelf then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato in the fridge.
